<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NYC Nov 2026 — Reni, Mateo &amp; Nico</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --ink:#0f0d0a;--ink2:#3a3630;--ink3:#7a7268;
  --paper:#faf8f4;--paper2:#f2ede5;--paper3:#e8e0d2;
  --red:#c8392b;--red2:#e85444;--gold:#c9922a;--gold2:#f5b942;
  --teal:#1a7a6e;--teal2:#22a693;
  --border:#d8cfc0;--border2:#c4b89e;
  --r:10px;--r-lg:16px;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;}

.hero{position:relative;height:100vh;min-height:580px;max-height:800px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496442226666-8d4d0e62e6e9?w=1400&q=85') center/cover no-repeat;}
.hero-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(12,10,8,.93) 0%,rgba(12,10,8,.5) 50%,rgba(12,10,8,.15) 100%);}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:48px 40px;}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold2);margin-bottom:14px;}
.hero-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(50px,9vw,86px);font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:.92;margin-bottom:22px;}
.hero-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold2);}
.hero-meta{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.hero-pill{background:rgba(255,255,255,.11);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-radius:24px;padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-weight:500;}
.hero-pill strong{color:#fff;}
.hero-scroll{margin-top:30px;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.hero-scroll::before{content:'';display:block;width:32px;height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.25);}

nav{background:var(--ink);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);}
.nav-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;padding:0 24px;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none;}
.nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
.nav-btn{padding:15px 20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .2s;}
.nav-btn:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);}
.nav-btn.active{color:#fff;border-bottom-color:var(--gold2);}

.page-section{display:none;padding:48px 0 100px;}
.page-section.visible{display:block;}
.container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;}

.section-header{margin-bottom:36px;}
.section-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:8px;}
.section-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,38px);font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.1;}
.section-sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:10px;max-width:560px;line-height:1.6;}

.filter-bar{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:32px;align-items:center;}
.f-btn{padding:7px 14px;border-radius:24px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--ink3);transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;}
.f-btn:hover{border-color:var(--ink2);color:var(--ink);}
.f-btn.on{background:var(--ink);border-color:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
.f-sep{width:1px;height:22px;background:var(--border);margin:0 2px;flex-shrink:0;}
.sky-toggle{display:flex;background:var(--paper2);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;}
.sky-opt{padding:6px 12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:transparent;color:var(--ink3);transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;}
.sky-opt.on{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}

.cards-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(295px,1fr));gap:20px;}

.pcard{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.pcard:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 14px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.1);}
.pcard.extra-card{border-left:3px solid var(--teal);}
.pcard-img{height:185px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;background:var(--paper2);}
.pcard-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .4s;}
.pcard:hover .pcard-img img{transform:scale(1.05);}
.price-tag{position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;backdrop-filter:blur(6px);}
.price-free{background:rgba(26,122,110,.88);color:#fff;}
.price-paid{background:rgba(201,146,42,.88);color:#fff;}
.price-other{background:rgba(50,44,36,.7);color:#fff;}
.day-chip{position:absolute;top:10px;left:10px;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;backdrop-filter:blur(6px);}
.extra-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal);background:rgba(26,122,110,.08);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.pcard-body{padding:16px 18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;flex:1;}
.pcard-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:5px;}
.pcard-cat{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:8px;}
.pcard-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:8px;}
.pcard-why{background:rgba(26,122,110,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--teal);padding:8px 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--teal);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:12px;}
.pcard-why strong{display:block;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px;opacity:.65;}
.pcard-footer{margin-top:auto;}
.maps-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--teal2);text-decoration:none;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:var(--r);border:1.5px solid rgba(26,122,110,.2);background:rgba(26,122,110,.04);transition:all .15s;margin-bottom:10px;}
.maps-btn:hover{background:rgba(26,122,110,.1);}

.rating-area{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:10px;margin-top:4px;}
.rating-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:5px;}
.stars-row{display:flex;gap:2px;margin-bottom:5px;}
.star{font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--border2);transition:color .1s;user-select:none;line-height:1;}
.star.lit{color:var(--gold2);}
.vote-row{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.vote-btn{padding:6px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--ink3);transition:all .15s;}
.vote-btn:hover{border-color:var(--ink2);}
.vote-btn.yes{background:#e8f5e9;border-color:#81c784;color:#1b5e20;}
.vote-btn.no{background:#fce4ec;border-color:#f48fb1;color:#880e4f;}
.vote-btn.maybe{background:#fff3e0;border-color:#ffb74d;color:#bf360c;}
.comment-field{width:100%;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px 10px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--ink);background:var(--paper);resize:none;min-height:52px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.comment-field:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--border2);}
.save-btn{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
.save-btn:hover{opacity:.8;}
.reviews-list{margin-top:8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.review-item{background:var(--paper2);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 10px;}
.review-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:3px;}
.review-avatar{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.review-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);}
.review-stars{font-size:11px;color:var(--gold2);margin-left:auto;}
.review-text{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.5;}
.votes-display{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2px;}

.day-block{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:14px;}
.day-block-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:16px 20px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:background .15s;}
.day-block-header:hover{background:rgba(0,0,0,.02);}
.day-color-bar{width:5px;height:44px;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
.day-block-info{flex:1;}
.day-block-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);}
.day-block-sub{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:2px;}
.day-block-toggle{font-size:20px;color:var(--ink3);transition:transform .2s;}
.day-block.open .day-block-toggle{transform:rotate(180deg);}
.day-stops{display:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
.day-block.open .day-stops{display:block;}
.stop-row{display:flex;gap:14px;padding:12px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);align-items:flex-start;}
.stop-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.stop-time{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink3);min-width:72px;padding-top:2px;flex-shrink:0;}
.stop-body{flex:1;}
.stop-name{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);}
.stop-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.5;}
.stop-price{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:12px;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.sp-free{background:rgba(26,122,110,.1);color:var(--teal);}
.sp-paid{background:rgba(201,146,42,.1);color:var(--gold);}
.sp-other{background:rgba(120,112,100,.1);color:var(--ink3);}
.stop-food{background:rgba(200,57,43,.05);border-left:3px solid var(--red2);padding:10px 14px;margin:0 20px 14px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:var(--red);}
.stop-food strong{display:block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px;opacity:.7;}

.user-selector{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.user-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:24px;border:2px solid var(--border);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink3);transition:all .2s;font-family:inherit;}
.user-btn:hover{border-color:var(--ink2);color:var(--ink);}
.user-btn.selected{border-color:var(--ink);background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
.user-avatar{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;}

.wishlist-form{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:28px;margin-bottom:28px;}
.wishlist-form h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:18px;color:var(--ink);}
.form-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.form-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;}
.form-field label{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;}
.form-input,.form-select{padding:9px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--ink);background:var(--paper);transition:border-color .15s;}
.form-input:focus,.form-select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--ink2);}
.form-submit{margin-top:4px;padding:11px 24px;border-radius:24px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;transition:opacity .15s;font-family:inherit;}
.form-submit:hover{opacity:.8;}
.wishlist-items{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:14px;}
.wish-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.wish-card-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;}
.wish-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.3;}
.wish-type{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;}
.wt-food{background:rgba(200,57,43,.1);color:var(--red);}
.wt-shopping{background:rgba(26,122,110,.1);color:var(--teal);}
.wt-museum{background:rgba(100,60,180,.1);color:#5b32c0;}
.wt-bar{background:rgba(201,146,42,.1);color:var(--gold);}
.wt-attraction{background:rgba(30,130,200,.1);color:#1872b4;}
.wt-other{background:rgba(120,112,100,.1);color:var(--ink3);}
.wish-addr{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink3);}
.wish-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink3);font-style:italic;}
.wish-who{display:flex;gap:5px;align-items:center;}
.wish-avatar{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;}
.wish-delete{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink3);opacity:.4;transition:opacity .15s;padding:2px;line-height:1;}
.wish-delete:hover{opacity:1;}
.empty-state{text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;color:var(--ink3);}
.empty-state .big{font-size:52px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.empty-state p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;}
.vote-notice{background:var(--paper2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);padding:11px 15px;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:24px;display:none;}

@media(max-width:640px){
  .hero-content{padding:28px 20px;}
  .hero-title{font-size:40px;}
  .container{padding:0 16px;}
  .form-row{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .cards-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .day-block-header{padding:12px 16px;}
  .stop-row{padding:10px 16px;}
  .stop-time{min-width:60px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Noviembre 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 3 personas &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8 dias</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Nueva<br><em>York</em></h1>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="hero-pill">✈ AA EZE→JFK · <strong>Sab 22 Nov 06:00</strong></span>
      <span class="hero-pill">✈ AA JFK→EZE · <strong>Dom 29 Nov 22:00</strong></span>
      <span class="hero-pill">🏨 <strong>Holiday Inn Chelsea</strong> · 125 W 26th St</span>
      <span class="hero-pill">👥 <strong>Reni · Mateo · Nico</strong></span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">Explorar el viaje</div>
  </div>
</div>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showTab('lugares',this)">Lugares</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showTab('itinerario',this)">Itinerario</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showTab('votaciones',this)">Votaciones</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showTab('wishlist',this)">Wishlist</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- TAB LUGARES -->
<div id="tab-lugares" class="page-section visible">
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:48px;">
    <div class="section-label">Guia completa</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Todos los lugares</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Fotos, descripcion, por que hacerlo, ubicacion en Google Maps, calificacion con estrellas y comentarios.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="filter-bar">
    <button class="f-btn on" onclick="fDay('all',this)">Todos los dias</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(1,this)">Sab 22</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(2,this)">Dom 23</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(3,this)">Lun 24</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(4,this)">Mar 25</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(5,this)">Mie 26</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(6,this)">Jue 27</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(7,this)">Vie 28</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(8,this)">Sab 29</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(9,this)">Dom 29</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fDay(0,this)">Extras</button>
    <div class="f-sep"></div>
    <button class="f-btn on" onclick="fCat('all',this)" id="cat-all">Todas</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fCat('mirador',this)">Miradores</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fCat('museo',this)">Museos</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fCat('barrio',this)">Barrios</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fCat('compras',this)">Compras</button>
    <button class="f-btn" onclick="fCat('gastronomia',this)">Gastronomia</button>
    <div class="f-sep"></div>
    <div class="sky-toggle">
      <button class="sky-opt on" onclick="fSky('ambas',this)">Ambas</button>
      <button class="sky-opt" onclick="fSky('con',this)">Con Skyview</button>
      <button class="sky-opt" onclick="fSky('sin',this)">Sin Skyview</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cards-grid" id="cards-container"></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- TAB ITINERARIO -->
<div id="tab-itinerario" class="page-section">
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:48px;">
    <div class="section-label">Dia a dia</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">El plan completo</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">8 dias de itinerario optimizado geograficamente desde el Holiday Inn Chelsea. Toca cada dia para expandirlo.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="itinerary-container"></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- TAB VOTACIONES -->
<div id="tab-votaciones" class="page-section">
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:48px;">
    <div class="section-label">Quien va a que</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Votaciones del grupo</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Cada uno indica si quiere ir o no. Asi coordinan sin mensajes de WhatsApp interminables.</p>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:28px;">
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:12px;font-weight:500;">Primero, selecciona quien sos:</p>
    <div class="user-selector">
      <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectUser('reni',this)" id="ubtn-reni">
        <div class="user-avatar" style="background:#c8392b;">R</div> Reni
      </button>
      <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectUser('mateo',this)" id="ubtn-mateo">
        <div class="user-avatar" style="background:#1a7a6e;">M</div> Mateo
      </button>
      <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectUser('nico',this)" id="ubtn-nico">
        <div class="user-avatar" style="background:#c9922a;">N</div> Nico
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="vote-notice" class="vote-notice"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="cards-grid" id="vote-cards"></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- TAB WISHLIST -->
<div id="tab-wishlist" class="page-section">
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:48px;">
    <div class="section-label">Sugerencias del grupo</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Wishlist colaborativa</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Hay algun lugar que quieran agregar al viaje? Sumanlo aca y que el grupo vote si ir o no.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="wishlist-form">
    <h3>Agregar un lugar</h3>
    <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:500;">Lo agrega:</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectWishUser('reni',this)" id="wubtn-reni" style="padding:7px 14px;">
          <div class="user-avatar" style="background:#c8392b;width:22px;height:22px;font-size:10px;">R</div> Reni
        </button>
        <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectWishUser('mateo',this)" id="wubtn-mateo" style="padding:7px 14px;">
          <div class="user-avatar" style="background:#1a7a6e;width:22px;height:22px;font-size:10px;">M</div> Mateo
        </button>
        <button class="user-btn" onclick="selectWishUser('nico',this)" id="wubtn-nico" style="padding:7px 14px;">
